sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Host App (e.g. Chat UI)
    participant Client as MCP Client (LangChain/LLM)
    participant Trans as Transport (Stdio/SSE)
    participant Server as MCP Server
    participant System as Local System / DB

    Note over App,Server: Phase 1: Handshake & Discovery
    Client->>Trans: init()
    Trans->>Server: InitializeRequest (Client Capabilities)
    Server-->>Trans: InitializeResult (Server Capabilities)
    Trans-->>Client: Process Ready
    
    Client->>Trans: tools/list
    Trans->>Server: Get tools list
    Server-->>Trans: [ {name: "execute_sql", schema: {...}} ]
    Trans-->>Client: Tools list
    Client->>App: Show "Tools Connected"

    Note over App,Server: Phase 2: Agentic Execution Loop
    App->>Client: User Prompt: "Get 5 latest users"
    Client->>Client: Reason (LLM): Need execute_sql
    
    Client->>Trans: tools/call {name: "execute_sql", args: {query: "SELECT * FROM users LIMIT 5"} }
    Trans->>Server: Forward Tool Call
    Note right of Server: Server validates JSON Schema
    Server->>System: Execute SQL
    System-->>Server: Raw Data (Rows)
    
    Server-->>Trans: CallToolResult {content: [{type: "text", text: "[{user1...}]"}]}
    Trans-->>Client: Tool Output
    
    Client->>Client: Synthesize (LLM): Finalize Answer
    Client->>App: "Here are the 5 latest users: ..."
